Week 1:

Day 1: Kubernetes Introduction

Read "Kubernetes Basics" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/tutorials/kubernetes-basics/
Watch "Kubernetes 101" video from the Kubernetes YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PH-2FfFD2PU
Day 2: Kubernetes Architecture

Read "Kubernetes Components" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/overview/components/
Watch "Kubernetes Architecture" video from the Kubernetes YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HlAXp0-M6SY
Day 3: Kubernetes Objects

Read "Kubernetes Objects" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/overview/working-with-objects/kubernetes-objects/
Complete the "Kubernetes Objects" tutorial from Katacoda: https://www.katacoda.com/courses/kubernetes/creating-kubernetes-objects-intro
Day 4: Kubernetes Deployments

Read "Deployments" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/workloads/controllers/deployment/
Complete the "Deploying Kubernetes Applications" tutorial from Katacoda: https://www.katacoda.com/courses/kubernetes/deploying-first-pod
Day 5: Kubernetes Services

Read "Services" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/services-networking/service/
Complete the "Kubernetes Services" tutorial from Katacoda: https://www.katacoda.com/courses/kubernetes/services
Day 6: Kubernetes Networking

Read "Kubernetes Networking" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/cluster-administration/networking/
Watch "Kubernetes Networking Demystified" video from the Kubernetes YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0Omvgd7Hg1I
Day 7: Kubernetes Resource Management

Read "Managing Compute Resources for Containers" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/configuration/manage-resources-containers/
Watch "Kubernetes Resource Management" video from the Kubernetes YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3zZsM2k2ngI
Week 2:

Day 8: Kubernetes Horizontal Pod Autoscaler

