Day 9: Kubernetes Persistent Storage

Read "Persistent Volumes" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/storage/persistent-volumes/
Complete the "Persistent Volumes" tutorial from Katacoda: https://www.katacoda.com/courses/kubernetes/persistent-volumes
Day 10: Kubernetes StatefulSets

Read "StatefulSets" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/workloads/controllers/statefulset/
Complete the "StatefulSets" tutorial from Katacoda: https://www.katacoda.com/courses/kubernetes/statefulsets
Day 11: Kubernetes RBAC

Read "Using RBAC Authorization" from the official Kubernetes documentation: https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/access-authn-authz/rbac/

